00:30:28,637 --> 00:30:30,297
Evet, heykel!

375
00:30:30,538 --> 00:30:32,027
Ralphie!

376
00:30:32,473 --> 00:30:36,408
Annem heykel ile aramıza
mesafe koymaya çalışıyordu.

377
00:30:36,644 --> 00:30:38,068
